Soup
30
Soup
image
Cauliflower, 1, stk
Onion, 1, stk
Water, 8, dl
Milk, 2, dl
Bacon, 200, g
Spring onion, 2, stk
Bread, 1, stk
Chicken stock, 2, stk

Cut the cauliflower into small pieces and chop the onion.
Add the cauliflower and onion to a pot with water and chicken stock.
Boil for 20 minutes.
Fry the bacon and spring onion and sprinkle over the soup.
Serve with bread.